---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Disclaimer"
  description="Affiliate disclosure, sponsored content policy, and accuracy disclaimer for Hexagamers."
>
  <div class="disclaimer-page">
    <div class="container">

      <header class="disclaimer-header fade-up">
        <p class="section-label">Legal</p>
        <h1>Disclaimer</h1>
      </header>

      <div class="disclaimer-body fade-up fade-up-1">

        <div class="notice-card">
          <p class="notice-label">Affiliate Notice</p>
          <p>
            This post may include affiliate links, including Amazon. This does not affect your viewing
            or any pricing on the associated sites, but we make a commission on purchases. This is how
            we help fund this site. Thanks!
          </p>
        </div>

        <section class="disclaimer-section">
          <h2>Advertising &amp; Monetization</h2>
          <p>
            <a href="https://hexagamers.com">hexagamers.com</a> is owned and operated by Hexagamers
            and may contain advertisements, sponsored content, paid insertions, affiliate links, or
            other forms of monetization.
          </p>
          <p>
            <a href="https://hexagamers.com">hexagamers.com</a> abides by word of mouth marketing
            standards. We believe in honesty of relationship, opinion, and identity. The compensation
            received may influence the advertising content, topics, or posts made in this blog. That
            content, advertising space, or post will be clearly identified as paid or sponsored content.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="disclaimer-section">
          <h2>Editorial Independence</h2>
          <p>
            Hexagamers is never directly compensated to provide opinion on products, services, websites,
            and various other topics. The views and opinions expressed on this website are purely those
            of the authors. If we claim or appear to be experts on a certain topic or product or service
            area, we will only endorse products or services that we believe, based on our expertise, are
            worthy of such endorsement. Any product claim, statistic, quote, or other representation
            about a product or service should be verified with the manufacturer or provider.
          </p>
          <p>
            This site does not contain any content which might present a conflict of interest.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="disclaimer-section">
          <h2>Accuracy</h2>
          <p>
            Hexagamers makes no representations, warranties, or assurances as to the accuracy, currency,
            or completeness of the content contained on this website or any sites linked to or from
            this site.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="disclaimer-section">
          <h2>Contact</h2>
          <p>
            If you have any questions regarding this policy or your dealings with our website, please
            contact us at <a href="https://hexagamers.com/contact">hexagamers.com/contact</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
.disclaimer-page { padding: 4rem 0 6rem; }

.disclaimer-header { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
.disclaimer-header h1 { margin-top: 0.5rem; }

.disclaimer-body { max-width: 740px; }

.notice-card {
  background: var(--amber-dim);
  border: 1px solid rgba(240,165,0,0.25);
  border-left: 3px solid var(--amber);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem;
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
}
.notice-label {
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--amber);
  margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
}
.notice-card p:last-child {
  color: var(--text-2);
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin: 0;
}

.disclaimer-section {
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding-top: 2rem;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}
.disclaimer-section h2 {
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.disclaimer-section p {
  color: var(--text-2);
  line-height: 1.75;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.disclaimer-section p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
.disclaimer-section a {
  color: var(--amber-light);
  text-decoration: underline;
  text-underline-offset: 3px;
}
.disclaimer-section a:hover { color: var(--amber); }
</style>
